quran[18{c,v,t}:
53,27,magar jo log akhirat ko nahi mantay woh firshton ko deviyon ke naamon se mosoom karte hain
53,28,"halaank is maamla ka koi ilm inhen haasil nahi hai, woh mehez gumaan ki pairwi kar rahay hain, aur gumaan haq ki jagah kuch bhi kaam nahi day sakta"
53,29,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jo shakhs hamaray zikar se mun pherte hai, aur duniya ki zindagi ke siwa jisay kuch matloob nahi hai, ussay is ke haal par chore do"
53,30,"inn logon ka mubalagh ilm bas yahi kuch hai, yeh baat tera rab hi ziyada jaanta hai ke uss ke rastay se kon bhatak gaya hai aur kon seedhay rastay par hai"
53,31,aur zameen aur asmano ki har cheez ka maalik Allah hi hai taakay Allah buraiee karne walon ko un ke amal ka badla day aur unn logon ko achi jaza se nawaze jinhon ne naik rawayya ikhtiyar kya hai
53,32,"jo barray barray gunaaho aur khulay khulay qabeeh af-aal se parhaiz karte hain, ila yeh ke kuch qasoor unn se sarzad ho jaye bilashuba tairay rab ka daman mughfirat bohat wasee hai woh tumhen uss waqt se khoob jaanta hai jab uss ne zameen se tumhe peda kya aur jab tum apni maaon ke piton mein abhi janeen hi thay pas apne nafs ki paki ke daaway nah karo, wohi behtar jaanta hai ke waqai mut-taqi kon hai"
53,33,"phir ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum ne uss shakhs ko bhi dekha jo raah khuda se phir gaya"
53,34,aur thora sa day kar ruk gaya
53,35,kya is ke paas ghaib ka ilm hai ke woh haqeeqat ko dekh raha hai ?
53,36,kya ussay unn baton ki koi khabar nahi pohanchi jo moose ke saheefon
53,37,aur uss ibrahim ke saheefon mein bayan hui hain jis ne wafa ka haq ada kar diya ?
53,38,""" yeh ke koi boojh uthany wala dosray ka boojh nahi uthaye ga"
53,39,aur yeh ke ensaan ke liye kuch nahi hai magar woh jis ki uss ne sae ki hai
53,40,aur yeh ke is ki sae anqareeb dekhi jaye gi
53,41,aur is ki poori jaza usay di jaye gi
53,42,aur yeh ke aakhir-kaar pohanchna tairay rab hi ke paas hai
53,43,aur yeh ke usi ne hansaya aur usi ne rulaya
53,44,aur yeh ke usi ne mout di aur usi ne zindagi bakhsh
